channel.title: Skype/Chat Me
channel.description:
Hey guys I'm going to start trying to develop a RSPS for probably the 6th or 7th time now. I really want to stay dedicated to this one so I was wondering if someone could help me?
Right now I'm on the basic first step; compiler. I've read on multiple sites/forums to use IDE like Eclipse. I have Eclipse but I'm not sure how to use it with my RSPS. I remember using it before with my RSPSs but I do not know how to configure my current version of Eclipse with my RSPS.
Please if someone could help me that'd be great. ;D
